{"tid":760397,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【期間限定】便利店首部可樂聲波震動機　幾秒即現沙冰","createTime":"2018-07-29T13:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T13:56:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"65f36d19884144578e89d20229e625de609f7459","tid":760397,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/food/daily/article/20180726/20460155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ffood%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F20460155&d=FNFkWGoRVOuIOJqBVYlf7QKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=c87f59c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ffood%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F20460155&h=e4f561a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/food/daily/article/20180726/20460155</a><br />\n<br />\n【期間限定】便利店首部可樂聲波震動機　幾秒即現沙冰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180726/large/26sub553new1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180726%2Flarge%2F26sub553new1.jpg&h=ed3db5aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n最近在便利店發現香港首部可樂聲波震動機，只要放置樽裝可樂，幾秒鐘就有沙冰出現，$15包可樂一樽玩一次，要先買代幣，再放入聲波震動機，按掣，燈熄掉就完成了。記者第一次試，沙冰效果不明顯，但一開蓋後，汽泡便迅速升高爆瀉，要即刻封口。要吃到更明顯的沙冰，有一個秘技，想知睇片啦。提提大家，聲波震動機只在三間便利店供應。<br />\n<br />\n供應地點：<br />\n1.屯門田景路31號良景邨良景商場1樓L101號舖7-Eleven便利店<br />\n2.長沙灣幸福邨商場地下17號舖OK便利店<br />\n3.馬鞍山新港城中心2樓2E-68號舖OK便利店<br />\n<br />\n記者：梁穎思、何嘉茵<br />\n攝影：伍慶泉<br />\n<br />\n即Like全新飲食專頁【籽想好食】：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/food.appleseed/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffood.appleseed%2F&d=FNFkWGoRVOuIOJqBVYlf7QKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=0c363634\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/food.appleseed/</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【專家教路】芝士點只分軟硬？　最重口味又係邊種？<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【台式食譜】台灣嫁到香港　煮媽媽三杯雞念家鄉味"},{"pid":"2d24fb102ea5484d842bbf8597dfb9d74731ed29","tid":760397,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4726cdeb555de299651a60f931a0875ff05f2b12","tid":760397,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:14:46.000Z","msg":"睇你老母片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6c7180353e393c1ce9998cb19d464b5738e2e5","tid":760397,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:27:04.000Z","msg":"沙冰效果不明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd0201ea752388b1c0f9addd0d095b3b3b562b3","tid":760397,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"買完樽可樂再比多15蚊玩沙冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd58c48ff5c2f5657c18373856d24c8f32bacb7","tid":760397,"uid":72608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5bd0201ea752388b1c0f9addd0d095b3b3b562b3","tid":760397,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"買完樽可樂再比多15蚊玩沙冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"原來15蚊包埋<br />\n柒左sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757eb124bb69d105df2f92a8a85b38ded1af8aa9","tid":760397,"uid":153570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"放其他飲品上去玩"}]}